fire 0.3b


This is a SDL demo with fire/flames and some other whirling effect.


Usage:

The following command line parameters are supported:

 -h : help
 -v : version
 -verbose : verbose mode
 -width <value> : width of the screen in pixels
 -height <value> : height of the screen in pixels
 -fullscreen : run in fullscreen video mode if possible


Author: Stephan Uhlmann 


Amiga 68k port by Piotr Bandurski


Changes:

0.3a:

- a lot faster
- hide mouse pointer in the fullscreen mode

0.3b:

- added "-verbose" option
  (old statistics are back)

0.3c:

- fixed some enforcer hits
